        <h3 class="mt-5">Phase 3 – Post Training Workshop</h3>
        <p>After completing the training in ITEES, Singapore the 100 participants attended a two day post training workshop in Bhubaneswar. The objective of the workshop was to scale the ITIs to a second level. While the 1st phase was to rejuvenate the ITIs, the 2nd phase of OSDA aimed at transform the society through Skilled In odisha.  In the post training workshop during 1-2 June, 2018, the participants enunciated the Mission, Vision and Values of the ITI institution and draw an concrete action plan.  All participants of the leadership development program were divided into 5 groups. Each group had 19-20 officials in them and was assigned with professional observer (Resource Person) from Industry with vast experience in organization development. After the whole two days of brain churning a new vision for OSDA was carved which is : “ Transform Society through Skilled Professionals”. </p>
